ain content homeoverviewabout usour teammanagement teaminvestment teamcontact uslogin overview bhr capital llc seeks to provide through a valueoriented investment strategy high absolute and riskadjusted returns with relatively low correlations to broad us equity and credit market indices we focus on eventdriven investment opportunities including special situations possessing one or more catalysts to unlock value we believe rigorous fundamental research coupled with various hedging strategies provides the most effective protection from capital losses the principals of bhr capital llc have substantial capital invested alongside our partners as we believe this is the single best way to ensure an alignment of interests copyright   bhr capital all rights reserved login  bhr capital skip to main content homeoverviewabout usour teammanagement teaminvestment teamcontact uslogin login login username  password  request new password copyright   bhr capital all rights reserved management team  bhr capital skip to main content homeoverviewabout usour teammanagement teaminvestment teamcontact uslogin management team michael n thompson managing partner and portfolio manager mr thompson founded bhr capital llc in  and is the portfolio manager for the investment vehicles managed by bhr capital llc  mr thompson is responsible for all portfolio construction security selection and risk management activities and oversees bhr’s investment team  prior to founding bhr mr thompson was with bay harbour management lc having joined the firm in  to lead research and investment efforts in the financial and real estate sectors and to manage the firm’s short investment portfolio  mr thompson was previously a managing director at wachovia securities with management responsibilities for a  billion propriety trading book  mr thompson graduated magna cum laude with a bba in international finance from the honors program at the university of georgia where he received alumni governor’s and hope scholarsh